<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Your OTP Code</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      body {
        background-color: #f4f6f9;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a73e8 0%, #1557b0 100%);
        padding: 40px 48px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .header p {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        font-size: 15px;
        margin-top: 8px;
      }
      .body {
        padding: 48px;
      }
      .body p {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #444;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .otp-box {
        margin: 32px 0;
        text-align: center;
        background: #f8f9fa;
        border: 2px solid #1a73e8;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 32px 20px;
      }
      .otp-label {
        font-size: 13px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        color: #1a73e8;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .otp-code {
        font-size: 38px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 10px;
        color: #1a73e8;
        font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 16px 24px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        display: inline-block;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(26, 115, 232, 0.15);
      }
      .notice {
        background: #e8f0fe;
        border-left: 4px solid #1a73e8;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 16px 20px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #1a4a8c;
      }
      .security-note {
        background: #fdf2f2;
        border-left: 4px solid #c0392b;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 16px 20px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-size: 13.5px;
        color: #7b241c;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #f9fafb;
        border-top: 1px solid #e8eaed;
        padding: 32px 48px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer p {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #9aa0a6;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }
      .footer a {
        color: #1a73e8;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .body,
        .header,
        .footer {
          padding: 32px 24px !important;
        }
        .otp-code {
          font-size: 32px;
          letter-spacing: 6px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Verification Required</h1>
        <p>Please use the code below to complete your action</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Body -->
      <div class="body">
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>
          We received a request that requires verification. Your One-Time
          Password (OTP) is:
        </p>

        <div class="otp-box">
          <div class="otp-label">Your Secure Code</div>
          <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
        </div>

        <div class="notice">
          ⏱ This code is valid for <strong>2 minutes</strong>. Please use it
          immediately.
        </div>

        <div class="security-note">
          🔒 For your security, never share this OTP with anyone. Our team will
          never ask for this code.
        </div>

        <p>
          If you did not request this verification, please ignore this email or
          contact our support team immediately.
        </p>

        <p>Thank you for using our service.</p>

        <p style="margin-top: 32px">
          Best regards,<br />
          <strong>The Support Team</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this address.<br />
          If you need help, visit our support center.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
